<tool id="fgenesh" name="FGenesH" version="1.0.0"> 
	<description>A gene finding software</description> 
	<command interpreter="perl">fgenesh.pl $input_fasta $models $output_fgenesh</command> 
        <inputs>
			<param format="fasta" name="input_fasta" type="data" label="Fasta file"/>  
			<param  name="models" type="select" label="Models">
				<option value="Monocots" selected="True">Monocots</option>
				<option value="Dicots">Dicots</option>
				<option value="MEDICAGO">Medicago</option> 
				<option value="Magnaporthe">Magnaporthe</option>
				<option value="Sclerotinia">Sclerotinia</option>
			</param>
        </inputs> 
        <outputs>
			<data format="txt" name="output_fgenesh" label="FGenesH result"/> 
        </outputs>
        <help>

**FGenesH : A Gene Finding Software**

-----

**What it does**

FGenesH : HMM-based gene structure prediction (multiple genes, both chains) 

-----

**Output format**

FGenesH raw data 

</help>
</tool>
